text: Joseph Maxwell Dempsie (born 22 June 1987) is a British actor. He is best known for his roles as Chris Miles in the E4 teen comedy-drama Skins (2007–2008) and Gendry Baratheon in Game of Thrones (2011–2019). Dempsie was born in Liverpool, England.
